                "Characteristics of meristematic cells",
                "Types: apical, lateral and intercalary"
            ],
            "teaching_strategy": [
                "Diagram explanation",
                "Concept mapping"
            ],
            "student_activities": [
                "Draw location of meristematic tissues",
                "List characteristics of meristematic cells"
            ],
            "assessment": [
                "Diagram evaluation",
                "Short answers"
            ]
        },
        {
